.Dd February 20, 2026
.Dt FLUXSNAP 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm fluxsnap
.Nd hotkey tiling helper for Fluxbox/X11
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl c Ar config
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
retiles windows inside monitor-visible workareas.
It honors EWMH
.Pa _NET_WORKAREA
so Fluxbox toolbar/slit space is respected.
.Pp
Default behavior per monitor:
.Bl -bullet -compact
.It
2 windows: even split
.It
3 windows: even thirds
.It
4+ windows: stacked across 3 columns
.El
.Pp
Default gap/border is 10px.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Fl c Ar config
Path to a configuration file.
.It Fl h
Show usage help.
.El
.Sh CONFIGURATION
.Bl -tag -width hotkey
.It Ic modifier
Super, Mod4, Alt, Mod1, Ctrl, Control, or Shift.
.It Ic hotkey
X keysym string (for example: space, F12, Return).
.It Ic gap
Pixels around and between tiled windows.
.El
.Sh TROUBLESHOOTING
If
.Nm
reports
.Dq BadAccess
for
.Dq X_GrabKey ,
the selected key is already grabbed by Fluxbox or another hotkey daemon.
Choose a different
.Ic modifier
or
.Ic hotkey .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr fluxbox 1
